    "2022] (for Hokkien, a dialect of Chinese).",
    "SCOPE & TRENDSThe focus of this survey is on NLP approaches that are aware of dialects: either in the form of the choice of the dataset, incorporation in the model or evaluation along dimensions involving dialect.",
    "The survey provides a broad introduction to past NLP research on dialects spoken in different parts of the world.",
